Interface ApplicationDetailsRepo

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<ApplicationDetails,Integer>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<ApplicationDetails,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<ApplicationDetails,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<ApplicationDetails,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<ApplicationDetails,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<ApplicationDetails>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<ApplicationDetails,Integer>
@Repository public interface ApplicationDetailsRepo extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<ApplicationDetails,Integer>
Repository interface for managing ApplicationDetails entities.

This interface extends JpaRepository, providing basic CRUD operations on the "ApplicationDetails" table. It also defines custom query methods for retrieving application details by application ID.

Custom queries in this interface are written using JPQL (Java Persistence Query Language) for flexibility in querying the database beyond the basic CRUD operations provided by JpaRepository.

Example usage:

 List details = applicationDetailsRepo.findAllByApplicationId(123);
